text: Vaccine injuries have been under-reported by one in 10, meaning that there may be 10 times more vaccine-related injuries than the yellow card scheme reports.
entity_strings: Vaccine injuries, under-reported, vaccine, yellow card scheme
entities: ['Vaccine injuries', ' under-reported', ' vaccine', ' yellow card scheme']

text: Millions of people have been injured by the vaccines.
Per the CDC, there are nearly twice as many vaccine-related deaths so far in 2021 (1,755) than all the vaccine deaths this past decade (994).
There are eight vaccine deaths per day.
